  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging, gory, intense!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way through a hostile urban environment, avoid getting killed by authorities and prepare for anything, even corpses coming back to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You probably should have stayed home, but it's too late for that...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336420/extras/43280cb410c4aadf17c0a0536d793b9e.poster.avif?t=1769532957\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336420/extras/43280cb410c4aadf17c0a0536d793b9e.webm?t=1769532957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336420/extras/43280cb410c4aadf17c0a0536d793b9e.mp4?t=1769532957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Die and retry mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 30-60 minute experience that can be completed in one sitting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rich (but dangerous!), detailed environment for players who love exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret endings, including a specific one for speed-runners!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
